<p>Here are a few recommended websites.</p>


<ul>
<li><a href="http://earthfriendlygardening.wordpress.com/" title="Sustainable Gardening for a Healthy Planet" rel="nofollow" target="_self">Earth Friendly Gardening</a></li>
