<li><a href="http://www.groxie.com/" title="Groxie is a blog about living a simpler, greener life. It's about making, not buying; it's about information, not marketing; it's about getting more out of less. This is DIY environmentalism." rel="nofollow" target="_self">Groxie</a></li>
